    "body": "This happens when you have run `eval \"$(starship init zsh)\"` many times either due to re-sourcing your config or something else. For a solution see: https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/3418#issuecomment-1711630970. \r\n\r\nNot really sure if starship needs to do the redundancy check on their part or not, but personally I think this solution works fine. ",
